title: Sophisticated Haven In A Premium Lifestyle Enclave - 9722 Lindsay P
posting_body: ['Capture The Charm, Love The Space, Live The Location', 'This exceptional home offers a modern interior, an abundance of natural lighting of the huge windows, and provides generous living spaces.', 'This thoughtfully designed and beautifully maintained kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, elegant countertops, custom white cabinetry, and a pantry area.', 'Retreat to the spacious master bedroom that boasts an ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet.', 'A design gem, the master bathroom is highlighted by a walk-in shower and double sinks.', 'Every bedroom has its own bathroom, too!', 'Other amenities include a separate laundry room with appliances and two fireplaces (indoor and outdoor).', 'The relaxing backyard features a covered deck.', 'A great spot for a morning cup of coffee or do your YOGA sessions while enjoying the greenery, nature view.', ' Enjoy community living in a desirable part of Rainier Beach.', 'The lot offers plenty of room to play.', "This unique home won't last long.", 'Schedule your private tour today.', '** Tenant pays for electricity, water, gas, garbage, and cable/internet.', '** Tenant(s) will be responsible for following any HOA-mandated “Rules & Responsibilities” and “Covenants, Conditions & Restrictions.”', '**', '** Tenant is responsible for any HOA Move in/Move out fees if applicable**', '** Security Deposit is equal to 1x the monthly rent based upon approved credit.', '(NOTE: In WA, security deposits have a maximum cap at 1x rent.', 'Allowed to have a separate and additional refundable Pet Damage Deposit equal to 25% of the monthly rent)', '**', 'If you are interested in applying, please email', 'show contact info', 'or text', 'show contact info', 'to request an application.', 'Please note that applications are reviewed in the order received and application fees are not refundable.', '**']
